Toronto-born actor Jonathan Crombie died on Wednesday night in New York after suffering a brain hemorrhage . 
  He was best known for his role as Gilbert Blythe in the Canadian television drama film Anne of Green Gables and two sequels . 
  Crombie was the son of former Toronto Mayor and Canadian Cabinet minister David Crombie  . 
  He was discovered at 17 in a high-school production of The Wizard of Oz . 
 